      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus obtained from tensile coupons machined from the same Ti-6Al-4V bar stock used for test constructs. CMM measurements of screw geometry provided dimensional inputs. Input uncertainty bounds established from coupon variability (n=5 per lot) and CMM measurement uncertainty, and propagated to obtain uval contribution."
    },
