      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-representative hardware. CMM inspection of all screws prior to testing confirmed dimensional conformance. Material certificates and lot traceability records retained. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison at the required credibility level."
    },
