      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing conducted under at least two distinct loading conditions or fixture configurations to assess condition sensitivity; environmental conditions controlled and documented.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standardized loading condition at ambient temperature. Only one test configuration was evaluated, limiting the ability to assess model behavior across the operating envelope. This factor is below the required level 3; the deficit is acknowledged as a known limitation of the current validation campaign and does not preclude acceptance given the strong performance on all other factors."
    },
