      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry as measured by CMM. Fixture stiffness independently measured and incorporated into the model. Material inputs matched to lot-specific coupon data. Equivalency between simulation inputs and physical test conditions confirmed at level 3."
