      "rationale": "Construct stiffness relates to subsidence risk; yield force relates to screw fracture risk; force at 40 mm displacement relates to catastrophic failure threshold. All three QoIs are directly referenced in the 510(k) substantial equivalence argument and are standard ASTM F1717 endpoints. Relevance rated at level 3."
